	%pi (cut-esg-wf (met/pair M1 M2) ([d] esg-wf/sg/pi (D1 d) (D2 d) DFS) ([d] [dm] mesg-wf/sg/pi (D3 d dm) (D4 d dm)) DL (esg-wf/sg/pi D1' D2' DFS) (mesg-wf/sg/pi D3' D4'))
